Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveSinger, Davido, has boasted about selling out his Boston show on Sunday, which is also Father’s Day.
Davido also shared photos from his ongoing ‘We rise by lifting others’ tour.
He tweeted, “Sold out Boston on Father’s Day!!!! Happy Fathers Day to all Stand up fathers worldwide !!!!!! BOSTON WAS A MOVIE!”
Boston is one of the stops on his North American tour.
